  "description": "The Alistigo document editor — pure, no UI. Takes an AlistigoDocument in, accepts commands (AddElement, DeleteElement, RenameList, …), produces events, folds them via the format package's projector, returns the updated document. The Application layer of the alistigo-ai system.",
